NOTES ON ARDUINO IoT

//References
	*https://www.circuito.io/blog/iot-projects/
	*https://www.instructables.com/id/Getting-Started-With-the-ESP8266-ESP-01/
	*https://www.instructables.com/id/ARDUINO-IOT-1/
	http://www.teomaragakis.com/hardware/electronics/how-to-connect-an-esp8266-to-an-arduino-uno/

//Popular components used for an IoT project
	*ESP8266-01 wifi module
	*ENC28J60 Ethernet module
	*HC-05 Bluetooth module
	*NRF24L01 Transceiver Module

//Steps in a porject
	*connect Arduino to IoT component (varies greatly by component)
	*Include library related to selected component
		i.e #include <ESP8266WiFi.h>
	*In code connnect to other device (phone, computer, etc.) using library